title: Dolphins doing well, Josh Rosen trade rumors, 2020 Free Agents (Football 3/29)
description:
Will Brinson and Sean Wagner-McGough break down the latest news and notes from around the NFL, including the Dolphins trading Robert Quinn to the Cowboys and what Miami might be doing, the latest Josh Rosen trade buzz, Greg Schiano leaving New England and then they look at the 2020 NFL free agent class.
